{"tid":1167865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨立運動三進路　第一推動獨立　第二使自身繼續存在　第三是記錄","createTime":"2019-05-23T10:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T10:17:05.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a25afa4b08e7ecc991a0a9699ea2f2bfd1bba4","tid":1167865,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1122338456691073025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1122338456691073025&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo4093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=ef2e7916\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1122338456691073025&h=30a3dc3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1122338456691073025</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1122338554472878080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1122338554472878080&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo4093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=ff1fbc71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1122338554472878080&h=78cfa274\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1122338554472878080</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1122338686706651136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1122338686706651136&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo4093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=6289e376\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F1122338686706651136&h=6fc24e40\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/1122338686706651136</a><br />\n<br />\n民族主義是很有市場的。是金錢賣買的那種有市場。只要世界繼續是全球化的，民族主義概念的商品都會受青睞，如汪洋大海中有一小點非常耀眼的反光。同樣是裙，但說蘇和蘭格仔裙，情況已不同。又例如同樣是食物，加日式二字。某個大中華膠老闆也是去日本開設港式茶餐廳，標榜港式。<br />\n<br />\n商業是變強的方法。以實力取勝的話，經濟 &gt; 政治 &gt; 武力。最理想是，所做的商業就是你在推動的東西。如果做到，一邊賣民族主義概念的商品，一邊推動民族主義運動，互相促進，就會是正向循環。<br />\n<br />\n對抗對家的理論、販賣民族主義概念商品，是使自身繼續存在，但做的都不是香港獨立。這是分三個進路：第一推動香港獨立；第二使自身繼續存在，就算一時做不了獨立，只要繼續存在，都可以再推動；第三是記錄，記錄想法、事情，記錄好，就算有此想法的人都消亡，都可以給予後來者資源，就像胡斯、馬文輝。"}]}